  <lyrics>[V1]
 Diosajj jaker munasinjja
 Munata Yokap qhitani,
 Acapach chlarnac mundoru
 Khanatatañapataqui,
 Uqhaman khespiyasistu.
 
[C]
 Diosar alabapjjañäni
 Jichhüru khana uruna.
 Diosan munasiñapata
 Jesucristow jutawayi. (Bis)
 
[V2]
 Cristojj jiwas munasinjja
 Cruzacamaw puriwayi.
 Jiwas laycu t'akhesisa
 Wilapa wartasiwayi,
 Wifiay jacañasataqui.
 
[V3]
 Diosan munasiñapajja
 Uqhamana khantawayi.
 Janiwa arumpiquiti
 Jiwasar jupajj munquistu,
 Jan ucast luráwimpiwa.
 
 </lyrics></song>